snippet: A crude oil tanker at the center of a dispute between Iraqi Kurdistan and Baghdad has reversed course from its route towards the United States, ship-tracking data showed on Friday, indicating that the shipper may not have a buyer....

headline.print_headline: Tanker With Piped Iraqi Kurdish Oil U-Turns Away From U.S.
headline.main: Tanker With Piped Iraqi Kurdish Oil U-Turns Away From U.S.

lead_paragraph: A crude oil tanker at the center of a dispute between Iraqi Kurdistan and Baghdad has reversed course from its route towards the United States, ship-tracking data showed on Friday, indicating that the shipper may not have a buyer.
